Create a Magic The Gathering card illustration of "Archon of Light Beer," depicting a muscular, jovial archon with glowing wings and a laurel crown, dressed in fratboy party attire—tank top, shorts, and sunglasses—soaring over a college campus party. He holds an oversized glowing beer stein aloft, and magical light pours from it, shielding a crowd of cheering college students below. The style is humorous and light-hearted, capturing the chaotic fun of a frat party with fantasy elements.